OpenView HD has secured a deal with Kwesé Free Sports for broadcasting in South Africa, as detailed in a report by Channel24. OpenView HD confirmed the accuracy of the report, which stated that Kwesé Free Sports will be shown on OpenView HD for free from 16 March. Kwesé Free Sports owns rights to several large sporting leagues, including the NBA, Major League Baseball, and Formula E. The channel will deliver quality sport from around the world that viewers will love, stated OpenView HD. “South African sports lovers looking for a diverse mix of exciting sporting action will be in for a real treat,” said the company.